CustomField.formula: (5 * ( FLOOR( ( DateValue(Custom_Settings_Scheduled__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8) ) / 7 ) ) + MIN( 5, MOD( DateValue(Custom_Settings_Scheduled__c) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8), 7 ) ) ) - (5 * ( FLOOR( ( DateValue(CreatedDate) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8) ) / 7 ) ) + MIN( 5, MOD( Datevalue(CreatedDate) - DATE( 1900, 1, 8), 7 ) ) )
CustomField.label: Days to Custom Settings Scheduled
